LUNCH (11:00-12:30) — Fuunji Tsukemen, Shinjuku
- 10:45: Queue at Fuunji (expect 30-45 min wait)
- Ticket machine: つけめん (tsukemen), 中 (medium)
- Rich fish-based dipping broth, thick noodles. Slurp loudly.

AFTERNOON (13:00-17:00) — Shrines & Towers
- 13:00: Meiji Jingu shrine — forested path, cypress torii gates, copper roofs.
