DINNER (18:00-19:30) — Afuri Yuzu Shio, Ebisu
- 17:45: JR from Shinjuku to Ebisu (2 stops, 5 min)
- 18:00: Afuri Ebisu — yuzu-citrus shio ramen. Lighter, aromatic, elegant.
  Perfect evening counterpoint to the heavy tsukemen lunch.
- 19:30: Evening stroll through Ebisu Garden Place (architecture + illumination).

=== DAY 2 (Sunday) — East Tokyo Linear ===

BREAKFAST (7:30-8:30)
