🚃 Transit: Suica card from airport (load ¥3,000). Works on everything.
💵 Cash: ¥15,000 from 7-Eleven ATM. Ramen shops often cash-only.
👟 Shoes: Comfortable. You'll walk 15-20km/day.
📱 Maps: Download Google Maps offline for Tokyo.
☂ Rain: ¥500 umbrella from any konbini. Tokyo doesn't stop for rain.
🙇 Manners: Slurp ramen (polite). Shoes off at shrines. Bow slightly.
